title: The Halloween Love Triangle and The Mysterious "L" Word
description:
Hi Friends!
Today on Murder, Mystery & Makeup, I wanted to talk about Peter and Betty Fabiano. Now if this doesn't sound like a Lifetime movie, then idk what one is. This isn’t lifetime though, its real life and boy did they get off the hook pretty easily. I Love and appreciate you guys so much and thank you for liking and subscribing, it means more than you know. I hope to be seeing you very soon and please be safe out there. Don't answer the door.
xo
Bailey Sarian
